{"tid":1023972,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"[歐化] 豐田新一代Hiace露出半個車頭","createTime":"2019-02-16T08:00:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-07T11:15:04.000Z","uid":51620,"like":4,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"1179ba9528661e21eaa4c5d052610b2680712e76","tid":1023972,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T08:00:47.000Z","msg":"如果閣下是手持2號車牌（輕型貨車牌）的話，那麼很大機會你考牌的戰車就是一部豐田Hiace。相信有開過Hiace的朋友都會知道它扁平的車頭令它睇位是多麼的方便和準確，因此在高速公路上一些開Hiace的司機大佬往往可以跟前車貼到盡，用盡馬路的每一分寸。<br />\n<br />\nHiace扁平的車頭雖則是方便睇位，不過同時間亦十分危險，事關整部車緩衝區就只有那一呎多的空間。因此當豐田設計全新一代的Hiace時，已全面放棄了這種扁平的車頭造型，取而代之的是歐洲式貨Van格局，比起以前多了半個車頭。<br />\n<br />\n當新一代Hiace的圖片在網上曝光後，不少Hiace忠粉都對新車表示「唔收貨」，更有人以為新Hiace是與標緻Expert合作做出來的。然而新Hiace不論是長闊高和重量都比現行Hiace多了不少，在攝位，泊位方面的確是少了一點優勢。不過據知新車將會配備一副280匹的3.5公升V6電油引擎或是一副177匹的2.8公升柴油Turbo引擎，相信這兩副引擎在力度方面應該能夠彌補新車多出來的515公斤吧。<br />\n<br />\n不過其實當不少香港用家都由Hiace轉用歐洲「有車頭」的貨Van的時候，豐田跟隨這個趨勢走也是情有可原吧。始終當安全標準越來越受用家所注意，「平頭」貨Van終有一日也難逃絕種的一天，大家只好接受現實吧。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190215/large/1550217132_9e36.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190215%2Flarge%2F1550217132_9e36.png&h=ecb99378&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20190216/59263454\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190216%2F59263454&d=zBdjJXAkzC5SgMGJ5jx7qstxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=ab39c3a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190216%2F59263454&h=ffaf9f57\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20190216/59263454</a>"},{"pid":"9e6abf6fdea10f94b396c546c5089661121b785f","tid":1023972,"uid":15646,"like":3,"dislike":14,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T08:05:07.000Z","msg":"舊款靚仔好多<br />\n改少少就已經可以好型"},{"pid":"d8932e9f3d66a61e7fe82ca5afa29e193bdee61b","tid":1023972,"uid":236709,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T08:10:48.000Z","msg":"講真豐田商用車係越改越hea<br />\n100系轉200系已經冇咁好揸<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n遲d應該一街歐洲van<br />\n30萬部vito咪話唔吸引<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73361bf0bbec1176df6942ac86b73c9b6abc7534","tid":1023972,"uid":32934,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T08:31:35.000Z","msg":"痴線, 咁仲叫hiace?"},{"pid":"d2bd42f626436a216a22f8788827cb25760c77e7","tid":1023972,"uid":51620,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"73361bf0bbec1176df6942ac86b73c9b6abc7534","tid":1023972,"uid":32934,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T08:31:35.000Z","msg":"痴線, 咁仲叫hiace?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T08:34:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />hiace 末日"},{"pid":"49d2b0d029235c88a5e93ddc1655a240dcbe93f6","tid":1023972,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T09:35:22.000Z","msg":"Caddy X JPN Taxi<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ea66fd1ddd0ebc7bef73ffc0c30ea52bf5d3491","tid":1023972,"uid":41154,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T15:49:29.000Z","msg":"舊hiace真係危險好多<br />\n宜家現代H1、VW Transporter咁受歡迎都係有原因，起碼呢啲車有車頭<br />\n<br />\n豐田都只係跟返大隊"},{"pid":"377280b19c00a6fc876a531394edd124b8ab867a","tid":1023972,"uid":169435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T15:59:37.000Z","msg":"出先算<br />\n佢歐洲敗走，要貼Logo賣車<br />\n<br />\n這架可能也是貼Logo, 不是自己生產"},{"pid":"b969d1a19580266979147c894d8ef026f5ac892f","tid":1023972,"uid":144949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T16:02:14.000Z","msg":"保養平就一定大把人用,個價二田一定最企<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06ce7024961ebe3b8e397bd884b4